text: Don't ever buy this. Bought 2 packets and all have since dropped from my walls. The sticky tape can be easily removed from the bumpers, maybe old stocks.
Range of gardening and BBQ products. They sell one of the best pricing for DIY Artificial grass.

Excellent weatherstrips! Saved my house from massive construction dust and smell, BBQ smell, smoking smell and noise. If you are suffering from any of these, go buy the weatherstrips. It's a lifesaver at an affordable price.

This Bukit Batok store is a warehouse not retail store. I would suggest heading down to their retail stores such as Coronation Plaza and Valley Point.
Found inside Bukit Batok Connection building ground floor.  Aside from gardening stuff they have equipment for BBQ and vaccum equipment for sale
Wow, the worst seeds ever. 100% zero germination - do not buy steve and leif seeds , everything i bought , many times, never germinates. And they are sold everywhere - terrible.
